description: Try our easy to follow Ham & Cheese Roll Ups recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Ham & Cheese Roll Ups Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 6 D'orsogna Premium Ham Off The Bone

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat the oven to 200Â°C (fan forced). Line a baking tray with parchment paper.
Roll out the puff pastry sheet and spread it with the tomato sauce. Add the ham slices on top and then sprinkle on the grated cheese.
Roll the pastry back up as tightly as you can. Cut the roll into 8 slices, each approximately 2cm thick and lay each one on the baking tray.
Brush the outside of the roll ups with the beaten egg. Bake for approximately 15 mins or until the pastry is golden brown.
Serve immediately, or let cool, freeze and store for up to 1 month.
